++ Friendly Data

FD is a HelpTheUser which means that the representation of [Data] should be in a simple and easy form.

++Examples

     Raw data such as dates can be made more friendly by using the language's terms for them:
    Tomorrow (Saturday 12th)
    Next Friday (Monday 18th), 8.30am - 12.30pm
    Monday 30th, ... 
    Tuesday 16th July, ... 
    Friday 26th October 2009
    Tomorrow Lunchtime

     Raw data such as numerical times can be demonstrated by clock faces.